dct_title_s: Debora et Barac defont et mettent en fuite Sisara général des armées de Jabin sur le torrent de Cison
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows illustrations of people, horses, and structures; depicts the biblical Battle of Mount Tabor.
Shows topography, vegetation, places of historical interest.
